o:317\n  | google3/go/context/detach.Go.func1\n  | \tgo/context/detach.go:250\n  | runtime.goexit\n  | \tthird_party/go/gc/src/runtime/asm_amd64.s:1736\nWraps: (6) RPC::DEADLINE_EXCEEDED: context deadline exceeded\nError types: (1) *go_utils.withTags (2) *withstack.withStack (3) *errutil.withPrefix (4) *withstack.withStack (5) *withstack.withStack (6) *status.statusError"
